Why C# ? 
1-Widely Used.
2-From Microsoft.
3-Large Community.
4-Open Source.
5-Multi-Purpose.
6-Multi-Platform.
7-Supports multiple Programming Paradigms (e.g. Procedural,OOP,Functional).
8-Is a modern object oriented.
9-Type Safe Programming Language.
10-Secure and Robust Applications.
11-Runs in the .net ecosystem.
12-Roots in the C Family.
13-Software Design Practices.
